                                                                "<h5>Largest Number: </h5>" + "<p>" + Math.max(...cleanArray) + "</p>" + "<br>" +
                                                                "<h5>Mean: </h5>" + "<p>" + (sum / cleanArray.length).toFixed(2) + "</p>" + "<br>" +
                                                                "<p><h5>Sum: </h5>" + "<p>" + sum + "</p>" + "<br>" +
